Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.02,0:00:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.69,0:00:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Where the heck are you taking me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.19,0:00:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit. Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.02,0:00:25.35,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,離せ！離せってばおい！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.69,0:00:27.61,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どこ連れてくんだよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.19,0:00:31.53,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ちくしょう…あにきぃーっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.41,0:00:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Betrayed this world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.46,0:00:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And it simmers within
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.80,0:00:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Rupturing my innards
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.76,0:01:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Swelling a reddish black
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.14,0:01:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Until the sun burnt skin ruptures
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.90,0:01:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a light  \N in the depths of the seething darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.66,0:01:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Confirming each other's voices  \N in the distance
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.83,0:01:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,As if to stroke with wet fingertips
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.04,0:01:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to touch you one day
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.76,0:01:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a light  \N in the depths of the darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.93,0:01:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Confirming each other's voices  \N in the distance
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.10,0:01:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,As if to stroke with wet fingertips
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.27,0:01:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to touch you one day
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.08,0:02:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,#22 The story of Nui
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.71,0:02:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What rotten luck. \NJust when I was almost at Daigo's castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.67,0:02:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You're stuck here too? \NIf you're leaving Daigo, you better hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.34,0:02:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,An amateur like you \Nshould get away while you still can.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.31,0:02:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Not me, though. \NI'm going to get rich out of this mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.39,0:02:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I have something to do here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.36,0:02:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure? There's a war brewing. \NWhat could you need to do here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.49,0:02:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I'm trying to find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.24,0:02:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,-Bro! Let me go, you jerks. \N-What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.28,0:02:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go of me. Hey, I said let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.37,0:02:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You big jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.96,0:02:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't scare me like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.93,0:03:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Dororo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.69,0:03:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get you back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.20,0:03:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,30 Asakura soldiers attacked, \Nbut retreated without much of a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.21,0:03:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,They must've been checking our defenses.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.46,0:03:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The main army has crossed Tatesugi Pass, \Nand should reach here in a day or two.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.09,0:03:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I will stop them here. They will not \Ntake a step into our territory.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.94,0:03:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You are well enough to get up, \NYoung Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.90,0:04:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't you stay rested?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.45,0:04:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,These are mere scratches. \NYou two are in a much worse state.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.87,0:04:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.62,0:04:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine, though. \NMy sister always hits me harder than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.42,0:04:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.88,0:04:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, where is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.76,0:04:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,She wasn't with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.39,0:04:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,No. But nobody will tell me why.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.18,0:04:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The doctor will know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.32,0:04:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,No, please wait Young Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.78,0:04:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You fool! \NWhy did you come with me to go fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.16,0:04:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you stay and rest?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.21,0:04:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You should've told me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.88,0:04:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,If only I had known...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.29,0:05:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And you wouldn't have gotten hurt. \NI'm coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.63,0:05:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,-No, Young Master! \N-Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.55,0:05:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,No. What if you catch the disease? \NWe can't let that happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.64,0:05:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You spoke well, Hyogo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.27,0:05:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me, Young Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.60,0:05:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,This disease, and now this wound.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.19,0:05:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I will not be able to witness \Nthe fulfillment of your ambitions.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.65,0:05:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The prosperous land of Daigo \Nthat you will one day establish.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.78,0:05:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But I know you will one day achieve it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.54,0:05:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.20,0:05:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyogo, you can still use \Nyour right arm, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.21,0:05:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,-Yes. \N-Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.42,0:05:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Protect Young Master with all \Nthat you have until your last breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.09,0:05:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.01,0:05:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I will avenge you. I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.01,0:05:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything that you tried to protect \Nwith your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.97,0:05:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I will protect.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.31,0:05:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.82,0:06:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Dang it, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.95,0:06:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.62,0:06:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Bro...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.37,0:06:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Please bro, stay the bro you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.89,0:06:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.23,0:06:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The castle is busy preparing for the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.32,0:06:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Now is your chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.66,0:06:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you the ones  \N being protected by him?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.46,0:07:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a hidden tunnel down this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.09,0:07:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You can escape from the castle in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.80,0:07:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure about this? You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.38,0:07:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I will not let another young child \Nbe sacrificed to protect us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.10,0:07:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,For how long have you traveled \Nwith my son, Hyakkimaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.02,0:07:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It must've been a harsh journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.48,0:07:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And with just you, a young child.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.57,0:07:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Won't you tell me about him?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.66,0:07:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? Isn't it too late for that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.62,0:07:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you forgotten what you told him?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.54,0:07:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,He was abandoned by his one and only mama,  \N and with those words.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.12,0:07:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,No eyes, ears, arms, legs, anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.50,0:07:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But he still tries really hard \Nto take back what is his.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.80,0:07:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Why does he have to \Ngo through all this, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.85,0:08:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.77,0:08:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I see the rain has cleared.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.90,0:08:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,My lady, I didn't expect to see you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.65,0:08:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The rain wasn't that heavy over at Banmon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.99,0:08:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not worry, my lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.70,0:08:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,His lordship will win and return safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.99,0:08:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Serve your lord well. You may go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.46,0:08:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,They're gone now. It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.97,0:08:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.84,0:08:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Let us hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.60,0:08:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a dead-end.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.78,0:08:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I chose Daigo's people and the land \Nover Hyakkimaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.32,0:08:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That cannot be undone, \Nno matter what I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.37,0:09:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I do not regret what I did  \N as a lord's wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.42,0:09:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you really mean that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.67,0:09:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Mutsu, I have brought you \Nyour medicine and food.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.88,0:09:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Mutsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.93,0:09:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Mutsu...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.69,0:09:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, so this is where it leads.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.65,0:09:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.86,0:09:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.69,0:09:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.99,0:09:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,When I heard there was a child with him,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.99,0:09:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt ever so indebted to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.04,0:09:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't do anything special...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.58,0:09:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, can I tell bro \Nthat you helped me escape?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.55,0:09:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.84,0:10:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.65,0:10:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Young Master, sis is gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.21,0:10:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Bro's mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.92,0:10:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.47,0:10:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder how it's going at Banmon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.05,0:10:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to be over there too \Nand win some honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.56,0:10:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.61,0:10:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.44,0:10:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Ghoul!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.21,0:11:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,My son, my child! Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.51,0:11:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,-Please...  \N -My son!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.55,0:11:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,My child!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.27,0:11:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You came with me on impulse, \Nbut are you sure about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.77,0:11:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Bro probably won't forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.23,0:11:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,-He might even... \N-If...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.03,0:11:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,If he chooses to kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.82,0:11:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That will be the path I must take.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.08,0:11:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like \NI finally understand something.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.17,0:11:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to see him again. One more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.30,0:12:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I will know what I must do when I see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.22,0:12:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,-The river! \N-It must be the rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.72,0:12:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The water is surging down \Nfrom the mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.94,0:12:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.36,0:12:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We're gonna crash!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.50,0:12:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Young Master, the person the guards saw, \Nit was my sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.83,0:12:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We must hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.18,0:12:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.35,0:12:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't eat me, I don't taste good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.36,0:12:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.69,0:13:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it, jeez!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.28,0:13:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,A horse?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.41,0:13:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear, dear. How lively it gets \Nthe moment you wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.58,0:13:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Priest!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.79,0:13:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You really are a lucky young'un.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.17,0:13:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The people here found you \Nafter you happened to be washed ashore.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.67,0:13:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.97,0:13:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey Priest, was there a lady with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.53,0:13:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,-I know, but... \N-Yahiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.41,0:13:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Dororo is up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.33,0:13:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally. Slept long enough. \NYou okay now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.95,0:13:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.87,0:13:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.83,0:13:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is she...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.08,0:14:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,When we told her about the invalids here, \Nshe asked to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.38,0:14:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We're lucky to have her. \NWe're short of hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.51,0:14:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,So hey, isn't she Lord Daigo's lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.77,0:14:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no way!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.27,0:14:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.03,0:14:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,These are all people \Nwho don't have a place to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.03,0:14:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Some had their savings \Nconfiscated for the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.49,0:14:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Some had their villages burned \Nbecause of epidemics.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.24,0:14:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We all have nowhere to go, \Nso we just stick together here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.25,0:14:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,All because of Daigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.63,0:14:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't do it out of spite.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.09,0:14:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,He did it because he believed \Nit would save the land.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.80,0:14:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You always talk like \Nyou understand everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.31,0:14:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,As for me, \NI'd tell that lady off if I could.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.81,0:15:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,-Jiheita. \N-I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.44,0:15:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But I feel so miserable \Njust sitting here like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.78,0:15:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,We're always tossed about \Nat the whims of the samurai.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.57,0:15:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't bear it much longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.83,0:15:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,There.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.00,0:15:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard you lost your mama, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.59,0:15:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheer up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.96,0:15:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Drifting downstream with Daigo's lady. \NWhat a dramatic entrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.18,0:15:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.01,0:15:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.39,0:15:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Eat up. You don't need your mama to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.12,0:15:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We won't be able to move on for a while. \NSeems like the castle is in an uproar.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.41,0:16:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I can imagine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.91,0:16:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,When my son was born, \NI am positive I heard him cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.17,0:16:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But right after, there was a white flash.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.59,0:16:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,When we could see again, he was already...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.90,0:16:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt he was the most precious thing \Nin my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.16,0:16:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Bro might turn into a demon \Nif we don't stop him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.04,0:16:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The demonic flame in him \Nis getting stronger and stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.04,0:16:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can't do anything about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.96,0:16:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.26,0:16:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.47,0:16:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Daigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.60,0:17:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Daigo's army is coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.98,0:17:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,-How was it? \N-Never seen anything like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.65,0:17:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,A full-blown army is up by the two pines, \Ngetting ready for war.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.07,0:17:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,All the soldiers that were left behind \Nhave joined them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.74,0:17:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,By the two pines? \NThat's just up that north cliff.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.04,0:17:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So what, is there another enemy \Nbesides Asakura?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.29,0:17:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.13,0:17:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But they're all really shaken, \Nlike they're scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.46,0:17:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.55,0:17:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,They're saying a demon is coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.47,0:17:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,A demon...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.10,0:17:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't recoil, attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.10,0:17:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let them reach the castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.36,0:18:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The twelfth demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.03,0:18:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The demon who could not devour Hyakkimaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.08,0:18:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You were denied what was yours...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.16,0:18:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Take me instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.71,0:18:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I give unto you my whole body.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.97,0:19:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, protect this land and its people!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.15,0:19:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,-Mutsu! \N-Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.94,0:19:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Stand back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.03,0:19:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you must not touch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.28,0:19:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you making a deal with the demons? \NI never wished you to!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.62,0:19:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I may not be able to fight with you, \Nbut my soul will stand with you and Hyogo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.75,0:19:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,For the people!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.04,0:19:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Sis...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.22,0:19:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,No, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.64,0:19:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,-What's wrong, Mutsu? \N-Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.60,0:19:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The contract between Daigo Kagemitsu \Nand the demons...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.60,0:19:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It can only be fulfilled...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.73,0:19:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,with the body of Hyakkimaru, \NDaigo's heir.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.25,0:20:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyakkimaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.67,0:20:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It might not be bro.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.51,0:20:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if it is, he's probably just \Nheaded for Daigo, and not...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.76,0:20:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, that thing you told me \Nabout when bro was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.14,0:20:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you tell it to him when we meet him?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.94,0:20:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So that he knows that his mama...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.91,0:20:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,really cared for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.83,0:20:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell him, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.92,0:20:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Give back Dororo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.30,0:21:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Back off!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.94,0:21:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.36,0:22:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyakkimaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.28,0:22:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,To complete the contract \Nand protect the prosperity of Daigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.41,0:22:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I will obtain your body, Hyakkimaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.71,0:02:12.92,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,チッ、ついてねぇ。醍醐の城は目の前だってぇのに…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.67,0:02:18.97,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あんたも足止めかい？\N醍醐を出るなら急いだほうがいいぜ？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.34,0:02:23.06,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あんたみたいな素人は、とっとと逃げ出すのが一番一番だよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.31,0:02:26.64,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,俺は、ガッポリ稼がせてもらうけどなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.39,0:02:30.65,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いや…わしも用がある
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.36,0:02:35.82,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,はぁー？すぐ戦が始まんだぞ？何があるってんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.49,0:02:38.57,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,それを…探しておってな
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.24,0:02:42.57,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにきぃー！痛ぇな、いい加減おろせって！\Nなんだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.28,0:02:47.45,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,このヤロー！離せってんだ！おい！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.37,0:02:49.54,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,バッカヤロー…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.96,0:02:52.54,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ケッ、おどかすなよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.93,0:03:05.76,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どろろ…！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.69,0:03:15.90,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,取り戻す！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.20,0:03:29.41,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,先ほど朝倉の兵30、深入りすることなく退いた模様
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.21,0:03:32.17,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おそらく、様子見かと。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.46,0:03:37.05,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,本隊は立杉峠を越え、一両日中には到着するかと思われます
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.09,0:03:43.22,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ここで食い止める。我が領地に一歩たりとも入れさせはせぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.94,0:03:59.61,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,若…動いて大丈夫なのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.90,0:04:01.86,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,もう少し寝ていたほうが…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.45,0:04:06.37,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,大した傷ではない。お前たちに比べれば、こんなもの
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.87,0:04:07.70,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そうか…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.62,0:04:16.63,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,俺は大丈夫。全然。姉上にどつかれるほうが、ずっとキツい
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.42,0:04:18.84,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そうだな…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.88,0:04:22.51,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そういえば、姉上は？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.76,0:04:24.93,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,一緒ではないのか
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.39,0:04:28.39,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いや…なんだか皆、はっきりしなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.18,0:04:32.77,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,医者に聞けばわかるだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.32,0:04:45.45,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,若！待ってくれ、若！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.78,0:04:50.87,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,この馬鹿者が！なぜ戦いに出た！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.16,0:04:52.87,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なぜ休んでいなかった！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.21,0:04:56.58,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ひと言…ひと言言ってくれれば。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.88,0:04:58.79,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,もっと早く気づけたかもしれぬ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.29,0:05:03.22,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ケガを負うこともなかったはずだ！\N入るぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.63,0:05:05.30,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ダメだ若！\Nどけ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.55,0:05:09.81,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ダメだ！もし若まで病がうつったら…それはダメだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.64,0:05:12.18,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,よく申した兵庫。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.27,0:05:14.98,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,申し訳ございません若。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.60,0:05:18.36,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,流行り病に加えて、この傷では…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.19,0:05:22.73,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,若が築かれる、戦のない醍醐の国
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.65,0:05:27.32,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,最後まで見届け申し上げることはもはや叶いませぬが、
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.78,0:05:30.58,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,必ずや若なら成し遂げられますこと、
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.54,0:05:33.45,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,この陸奥は信じておりまする
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.20,0:05:36.96,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,兵庫。右の腕はまだ動くな
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.21,0:05:38.88,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,はい\Nならばよい。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.42,0:05:44.21,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,その身の動くかぎり、最後の最後まで若をお守り申し上げよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.09,0:05:45.92,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.01,0:05:49.05,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,報いるぞ…必ず…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.01,0:05:52.85,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そなたが命をかけても守ろうとした全て。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.97,0:05:55.64,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,私が、必ず！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.31,0:05:58.56,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,守り抜いてみせる！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.82,0:06:05.53,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,この…このやろ…この…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.95,0:06:10.66,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,やっぱダメかぁ…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.62,0:06:13.49,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにき…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.37,0:06:24.17,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにき…お願いだから、あにきのままでいてくれよ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.89,0:06:34.89,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あ…あんたは
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.23,0:06:43.69,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,戦の支度で城内がざわついています。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.32,0:06:45.32,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,今のうちです
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.66,0:06:53.91,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なぜ貴様らが若に助けられている！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.46,0:07:03.79,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,少し先に隠し通路があります。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.09,0:07:06.46,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そこからならば城の外へ抜けられます
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.80,0:07:08.97,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いいのかよ！あんたはだって…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.38,0:07:13.55,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,もうこれ以上、幼子を盾にする必要はありません。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.10,0:07:20.14,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あなたは…いつからあの子…百鬼丸と旅をしているのですか？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.02,0:07:23.36,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,さぞや過酷な旅であったと…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.48,0:07:25.86,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あなたのような幼子とずっと2人で。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.57,0:07:30.86,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,教えてはもらえませんか。あの子のことを
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.66,0:07:34.32,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,今さらそんなん知ってどうすんだよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.62,0:07:36.87,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,自分が何言ったのか覚えてねぇのかよ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.54,0:07:42.08,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,たった1人のおっかちゃんに捨てられて…あんなことまで…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.12,0:07:46.38,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,目も耳も、腕も足もなんもなくて。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.50,0:07:50.17,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,それでも取られたもん取り戻そうって必死に戦ってきて
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.80,0:07:53.76,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なんであにきばっかりあんな目に遭わされなきゃなんないんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.85,0:08:00.68,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ヤバい…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.77,0:08:05.77,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,雨は止んだようですね
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.90,0:08:09.23,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,これは、御方様。このような所で。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.65,0:08:12.57,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ばんもんのほうは左程の降りではなかったようです。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.99,0:08:14.20,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ご安心くださいませ。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.70,0:08:17.49,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,殿は必ず勝ってお戻りになりますゆえ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.99,0:08:22.79,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,殿のため存分に働くのですよ。ゆきなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.46,0:08:28.38,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,もうゆきましたよ。さ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.97,0:08:33.47,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おっかちゃん…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.84,0:08:36.68,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,急ぎましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.60,0:08:45.35,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,い、行き止まりじゃ…あっ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.78,0:08:55.20,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,わたくしは醍醐の国と民を取り、百鬼丸を捨てました。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.32,0:08:58.41,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,それはもう、何があろうと覆りはしない
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.37,0:09:04.12,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,領主の妻として、わたくしは悔いはしません
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.42,0:09:07.13,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ホントにそう思ってんのかい
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.67,0:09:14.30,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,陸奥どの。薬と食事を持って参りました…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.88,0:09:16.93,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,陸奥どの
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.93,0:09:19.97,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,陸奥どの？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.69,0:09:28.73,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,へぇー、こんなところに
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.65,0:09:31.15,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,気をつけておゆきなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.86,0:09:33.57,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あぁ…あの…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.69,0:09:34.65,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.99,0:09:38.41,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あの子と旅をしている子供がいると聞いて、
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.99,0:09:43.45,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,本当にわたくしは…あなたにどれだけ感謝してもし足りない
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.04,0:09:47.54,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お…おいらは、別に…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.58,0:09:54.17,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あっ、そうだ！あにきにさ、\Nあにきのおっかちゃんが助けてくれたって言ってもいいかな！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.55,0:09:56.88,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,それは…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.84,0:10:01.43,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あぁ…じゃ、またな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.65,0:10:16.44,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,若！姉上が！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.21,0:10:32.59,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あ…あにきのおっかちゃん！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.92,0:10:33.96,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,わたくしも…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.47,0:10:41.93,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ばんもんのほうはどうなってっかなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.05,0:10:44.97,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おらっちもあっちで手柄立てたかったぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.56,0:10:50.35,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なんだ？ありゃ…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.61,0:10:55.82,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あ、ありゃ…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.44,0:10:57.82,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,物の怪？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.21,0:11:17.84,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,坊や…！坊や…！坊や！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.51,0:11:20.84,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,御方様！\N坊やぁ！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.55,0:11:23.60,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,坊やぁ…！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.27,0:11:32.40,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なぁ…勢いでつい来ちゃったけど、ホント…いいのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.77,0:11:36.98,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにきは多分あんたを許さない。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.23,0:11:38.57,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,それどころか\Nもし…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.03,0:11:40.82,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あの子に斬られるのであれば
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.82,0:11:45.53,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,それがおそらく、わたくしの成すべきことなのでしょう。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.08,0:11:49.95,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ようやく一つだけわかったような気がします
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.17,0:11:56.96,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,わたくしは…あの子に会いたかったのです。もう一度…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.30,0:12:03.09,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,わたくしのこれから成すべきことも、そこで初めて。きっと…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.22,0:12:09.60,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,わっ！川の流れが！\N昼間の雨のせいで！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.72,0:12:12.60,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,山から一度に水が流れてきたのです！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.94,0:12:15.73,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ちくしょう…曲がれ…曲がれ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.36,0:12:19.23,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ぶ、ぶつかるー！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.50,0:12:35.08,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,若！門兵が見ていた！姉上は、やはり！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.83,0:12:36.88,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,急ぐぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.18,0:12:51.22,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,はぁ…へっへへ…やめろよ…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.35,0:12:54.89,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おいら、食ってもうまく…ねぇよ…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.36,0:12:59.61,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お、おい！ひぃやぁあ～っ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.69,0:13:04.86,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,や…やめろってんだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.28,0:13:08.12,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あ…う…馬？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.41,0:13:13.87,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,やれやれ、目覚めた途端に賑やかなこった
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.58,0:13:15.67,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,坊さん！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.79,0:13:18.75,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お前さんもよっぽど悪運が強いねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.17,0:13:23.38,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ここの連中が、偶然流れ着いたのを拾ってくれたようだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.67,0:13:25.51,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ここは？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.97,0:13:33.43,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あっ！坊さん！おいらと一緒に女の人が…いなかったかい？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.53,0:13:47.91,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,弥彦！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.41,0:13:50.24,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どろろが目を覚ました
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.33,0:13:53.83,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,やっとお目覚めか。大丈夫かい？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.95,0:13:55.25,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あ、あぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.87,0:13:57.79,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,えっ？ありゃあ…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.83,0:13:59.96,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なんで…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.08,0:14:04.80,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ここの病人たちの話を聞いたら手伝わせてくれって。自分からよ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.38,0:14:08.89,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,我々も手が足りぬからな。ありがたい
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.51,0:14:14.47,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なぁ、あの人もしかして…醍醐の奥方じゃあねぇのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.77,0:14:17.14,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いっ…ちっ…違わい！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.27,0:14:18.69,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そうかい。フッ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.03,0:14:27.90,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,みんな行き場を無くした連中でさ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.03,0:14:30.37,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,戦のために蓄え取られたり
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.49,0:14:33.45,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,流行り病いが出たって村ごと焼き払われたり
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.24,0:14:38.58,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どこにも行く当てがなくなって、こうして身を寄せ合ってるわけよ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.25,0:14:40.50,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,醍醐のせいで…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.63,0:14:44.59,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,醍醐景光とて、民が憎くてしたことではあるまい。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.09,0:14:49.05,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,国を守るため、彼なりに考えた上での行動だろう
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.80,0:14:53.68,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,道秀はすぐ悟ったようなことを言いやがる。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.31,0:14:58.56,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,俺、本当はあの奥方にだってガツッと言ってやりてぇんだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.81,0:15:01.10,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,次平太\Nわかってる！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.44,0:15:06.36,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,けどよ…このまんまじゃ、俺たちあんまり…みじめじゃねぇかよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.78,0:15:10.86,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,侍どもの都合で、俺らはいっつも振り回され続け…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.57,0:15:13.12,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,たまんねぇよな…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.00,0:15:23.13,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,聞いたぜ。お前もおっかちゃん、亡くしちまったんだってな
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.59,0:15:27.38,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,元気出せ。な
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.96,0:15:33.05,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,醍醐の奥方と川流れたぁ、また派手な真似したもんだねぇ。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.18,0:15:34.93,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,これからどうするんだい
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.01,0:15:39.48,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,今…考えてんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.39,0:15:46.36,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いっぱい食えよ…おっかちゃんがいなくたって…生きてゆけらぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.12,0:15:59.50,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,しばらく、ここで足止めだ。城のほうは大騒ぎらしい
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.41,0:16:01.41,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,でしょうね
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.91,0:16:07.67,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あの子が生まれたとき、わたくしはあの子の産声を確かに聞いたのです
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.17,0:16:11.92,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,その直後、辺りが真っ白になり…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.59,0:16:15.85,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,光が去ったときにはもう…あの子は…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.90,0:16:36.49,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,限りなく…愛おしいと思いました
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.16,0:16:42.62,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにきは…このままじゃ鬼神になっちまうかもしれない
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.04,0:16:47.34,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにきの中の鬼神の炎がどんどん強くなってるんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.04,0:16:50.84,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,けど…おいらじゃどうにもできなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.96,0:16:51.96,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そんな！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.26,0:16:55.22,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,でも…もしかしたら！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.47,0:16:58.10,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,醍醐だぁ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.60,0:17:01.35,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,醍醐の兵が来たぞぉ！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.98,0:17:07.61,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,それで\Nともかく！今まであんなの見たことねぇよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.65,0:17:13.95,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,二本松の丘に、山ほど醍醐の兵が集まって戦の支度を始めてる。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.07,0:17:17.62,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,山城に残っていたのが全部駆り出されたみてぇだ…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.74,0:17:21.29,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,二本松って言やぁ、北の崖登ったすぐ先じゃねぇか！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.04,0:17:26.17,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,で朝倉の他に敵が現れたのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.29,0:17:27.58,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,よくわからねぇ。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.13,0:17:32.34,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ただ、やけに焦ってるって言うか…怯えてるみたいな…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.46,0:17:33.42,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,怯えてる？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.55,0:17:35.59,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なんでも、鬼神が来るって…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.47,0:17:38.43,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,鬼神！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.10,0:17:43.85,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,今だ！撃てぇー！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.10,0:17:47.81,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,近づけるなぁ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.36,0:18:39.41,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,12体目の鬼神…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.03,0:18:44.45,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,かつて…百鬼丸より身体を奪えなかった鬼神よ。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.08,0:18:47.58,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,果たされなかったその約定、今…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.16,0:18:50.92,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,私が代わりに！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.71,0:18:57.84,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,この身体のすべてをお前に捧げる。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.97,0:19:02.35,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どうか…我らの国を。皆を！守りたまえ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.15,0:19:12.44,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,陸奥！\N姉上！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.94,0:19:14.40,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,来てはなりませぬ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.03,0:19:19.15,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いけません、若！私に触れては！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.28,0:19:22.91,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,鬼神と取り引きするつもりか！勝手なことを！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.62,0:19:29.54,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おそばで戦えなくとも…私の魂は若と兵庫とともに醍醐を…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.75,0:19:30.92,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,民を！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.04,0:19:32.29,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,姉上！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.22,0:19:42.68,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なっ…！そ、そんな…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.64,0:19:45.47,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どうした陸奥！\N姉上！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.60,0:19:50.73,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,醍醐と…鬼神たちの…約定は…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.60,0:19:53.48,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,醍醐の…跡取りである…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.73,0:19:58.23,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,百鬼丸の…身体でのみ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.25,0:20:11.71,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,百っ鬼丸ぅー！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.67,0:20:20.13,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,まだあにきだって決まったわけじゃねぇ。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.51,0:20:24.93,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにきだとしても、ただ醍醐を目指してるだけで…まだ…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.76,0:20:32.02,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なぁ。さっき言ってたよな。あにきが生まれたときのこと
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.14,0:20:37.40,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あれ…あにきに会えたら、直接言ってやってくれねぇか
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.94,0:20:44.20,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おっかちゃんは…あにきのことをちゃんと…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.91,0:20:47.16,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,大切に思ってたって
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.83,0:20:52.04,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにきに伝えてやってくれよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.92,0:20:58.92,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どろろを…返せ！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.30,0:21:00.42,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,知るか！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.94,0:21:59.31,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,それは…俺のものだぁー！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.36,0:22:03.57,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,百っ鬼丸ぅー！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.28,0:22:17.04,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,約定を果たし…醍醐の国を永劫守るために。
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.41,0:22:21.71,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,貴様の身体、貰い受ける！百鬼丸！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.70,0:22:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Born into this world
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.37,0:22:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no salvation
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.95,0:22:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The distorted shape of the heart
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.33,0:23:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet it beats courageously
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.88,0:23:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no turning back
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.88,0:23:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Even from the path of evil
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.92,0:23:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Witnessing the withering seasons
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.34,0:23:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We search for the truth
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.43,0:23:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,In our ugliness
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.27,0:23:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't even recognize the pain
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.90,0:23:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,As we peel back the skin
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.82,0:23:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We are forever tormented by our stupidity
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.45,0:23:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But if the dawn never comes
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.95,0:23:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Through the painful night
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.08,0:23:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You who distrusts nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.37,0:23:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You will be able to love  \N this accursed world
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.25,0:23:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that we carry the world  \N on our shoulders
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.67,0:23:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time to take it back
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.97,0:24:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,"Mutsu and Hyogo"
